      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed comprehensively across all inputs including fluid viscosity, hemolysis power-law exponents alpha and beta, and geometric tolerances. Input distributions drawn from literature. Propagated UQ envelope reported at all 5 operating points. Achieved level meets near-required but geometry tolerance distributions rely on manufacturer spec sheets rather than measured data."
